      <guid>https://crazymilk.net/blog/white-cross-again.html</guid>
      <link>https://crazymilk.net/blog/white-cross-again.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <img src="https://crazymilk.net/files/images/photos/white-cross-again.webp" alt="View of a lake on an overcast day. Green pasture dotted with yellow flowers is in the foreground together with a park bench under a large white cross. The sky is completely covered in clouds." width=960 height=540 loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
